casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Ben Elton BRUNER.
No. D-3053.
Supreme Court of the United States
Aug. 23, 2019.
Ben Elton Bruner, of Opelika, Alabama, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
